					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">WedNESday wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">However, how does the NES know if that PPU area is VROM or VRAM? Is there some kind of flag somewhere?</div>
<br />
<br />It doesn't - to the NES, VRAM and VROM are the same, the only difference being that writing to VRAM actually does something (i.e. the value stored in it changes).</div>

					
