				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There's also the fact that CHR ROM and CHR RAM are <strong>not</strong> mutually exclusive - several mappers, one of which is used in the games "Pin-Bot" and "High Speed" (NES-TQROM, in case you're wondering) makes use of both CHR ROM and CHR RAM side by side, using an upper bank bit to select between ROM and RAM in each region.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
					<br clear="all" /><br />

